itunes:summary:
Derek Weida welcomes special guest Chad Cole who runs Crossfit Apollo in Las Vegas and discusses Chad’s experiences at the Crossfit Games, the training rigor he had to endure to get there, what his life was like after training for the Crossfit Games, and talk about how Crossfit training and fatherhood work together.
